{
  "number": 56,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الوَاقِعَةِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Waaqia",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Inevitable",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 4980,
      "text": "WHEN THAT which must come to pass [at last] comes to pass,",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4981,
      "text": "there will be nought that could give the lie to its having come to pass,",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4982,
      "text": "abasing [some], exalting [others]!",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4983,
      "text": "When the earth is shaken with a shaking [severe],",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4984,
      "text": "and the mountains are shattered into [countless] shards,",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4985,
      "text": "so that they become as scat­tered dust –",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4986,
      "text": "[on that Day,] then, shall you be [divided into] three kinds.",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4987,
      "text": "Thus, there shall be such as will have attained to what is right: oh, how [happy] will be they who have attained to what is right!",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4988,
      "text": "And there shall be such as will have lost them­selves in evil: oh, how [unhappy] will be they who have lost themselves in evil!",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4989,
      "text": "But the foremost shall be [they who in life were] the foremost [in faith and good works]:",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4990,
      "text": "they who were [always] drawn close unto God!",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4991,
      "text": "In gardens of bliss [will they dwell] -",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4992,
      "text": "a good many of those of olden times,",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4993,
      "text": "but [only] a few of later times.",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4994,
      "text": "[They will be seated] on gold-encrusted thrones of happiness,",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4995,
      "text": "reclining upon them, facing one another [in love].",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4996,
      "text": "Immortal youths will wait upon them",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4997,
      "text": "with goblets, and ewers, and cups filled with water from unsullied springs",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4998,
      "text": "by which their minds will not be clouded and which will not make them drunk;",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4999,
      "text": "and with fruit of any kind that they may choose,",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5000,
      "text": "and with the flesh of any fowl that they may desire.",
      "numberInSurah": 21,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5001,
      "text": "And [with them will be their] companions pure, most beautiful of eye,",
      "numberInSurah": 22,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5002,
      "text": "like unto pearls [still] hidden in their shells.",
      "numberInSurah": 23,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5003,
      "text": "[And this will be] a reward for what they did [in life].",
      "numberInSurah": 24,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5004,
      "text": "No empty talk will they hear there, nor any call to sin,",
      "numberInSurah": 25,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5005,
      "text": "but only the tiding of inner soundness and peace.",
      "numberInSurah": 26,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5006,
      "text": "NOW AS FOR those who have attained to righteous­ness - what of those who have attained to righteous­ness?",
      "numberInSurah": 27,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5007,
      "text": "[They, too, will find themselves] amidst fruit- laden lote-trees,",
      "numberInSurah": 28,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5008,
      "text": "and acacias flower-clad,",
      "numberInSurah": 29,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5009,
      "text": "and shade extended,",
      "numberInSurah": 30,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5010,
      "text": "and waters gushing,",
      "numberInSurah": 31,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5011,
      "text": "and fruit abounding,",
      "numberInSurah": 32,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5012,
      "text": "never-failing and never out of reach.",
      "numberInSurah": 33,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5013,
      "text": "And [with them will be their] spouses, raised high:",
      "numberInSurah": 34,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5014,
      "text": "for, behold, We shall have brought them into being in a life renewed,",
      "numberInSurah": 35,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5015,
      "text": "having resurrected them as virgins,",
      "numberInSurah": 36,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5016,
      "text": "full of love, well-matched",
      "numberInSurah": 37,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5017,
      "text": "with those who have attained to righteousness:",
      "numberInSurah": 38,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5018,
      "text": "a good many of olden times,",
      "numberInSurah": 39,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5019,
      "text": "and a good many of later times.",
      "numberInSurah": 40,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5020,
      "text": "BUT AS FOR those who have persevered in evil - what of those who have persevered in evil?",
      "numberInSurah": 41,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5021,
      "text": "[They will find themselves] in the midst of scorching winds, and burning despair,",
      "numberInSurah": 42,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5022,
      "text": "and the shadows of black smoke -",
      "numberInSurah": 43,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5023,
      "text": "[shadows] neither cooling nor soothing.",
      "numberInSurah": 44,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5024,
      "text": "For, behold, in times gone by they were wont to abandon themselves wholly to the pursuit of pleasures,",
      "numberInSurah": 45,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5025,
      "text": "and would persist in heinous sinning,",
      "numberInSurah": 46,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5026,
      "text": "and would say, “What! After we have died and become mere dust and bones, shall we, forsooth, be raised from the dead? -",
      "numberInSurah": 47,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5027,
      "text": "and perhaps, too, our forebears of old?”",
      "numberInSurah": 48,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5028,
      "text": "Say: “Verily, those of olden times and those of later times",
      "numberInSurah": 49,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5029,
      "text": "will indeed be gathered together at an appointed time on a Day known [only to God]:",
      "numberInSurah": 50,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5030,
      "text": "and then, verily, O you who have gone astray and called the truth a lie,",
      "numberInSurah": 51,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5031,
      "text": "you will indeed have to taste of the tree of deadly fruit,",
      "numberInSurah": 52,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5032,
      "text": "and will have to fill your bellies therewith,",
      "numberInSurah": 53,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5033,
      "text": "and will thereupon have to drink [many a draught] of burning despair -",
      "numberInSurah": 54,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5034,
      "text": "drink it as the most insatiably thirsty camels drink!”",
      "numberInSurah": 55,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5035,
      "text": "Such will be their welcome on Judgment Day!",
      "numberInSurah": 56,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5036,
      "text": "WE who have created you, [O men:] why, then, do you not accept the truth?",
      "numberInSurah": 57,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5037,
      "text": "Have you ever considered that [seed] which you emit?",
      "numberInSurah": 58,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5038,
      "text": "Is it you who create it - or are We the source of its creation?",
      "numberInSurah": 59,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5039,
      "text": "We have [indeed] decreed that death shall be [ever-present] among you: but there is nothing to prevent Us",
      "numberInSurah": 60,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5040,
      "text": "from changing the nature of your existence and bringing you into being [anew] in a manner [as yet] unknown to you.",
      "numberInSurah": 61,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5041,
      "text": "And [since] you are indeed aware of the [miracle of your] coming into being in the first instance - why, then, do you not bethink yourselves [of Us]?",
      "numberInSurah": 62,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5042,
      "text": "Have you ever considered the seed which you cast upon the soil?",
      "numberInSurah": 63,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5043,
      "text": "Is it you who cause it to grow - or are We the cause of its growth?",
      "numberInSurah": 64,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5044,
      "text": "[For,] were it Our will, We could indeed turn it into chaff, and you would be left to wonder [and to lament],",
      "numberInSurah": 65,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5045,
      "text": "“Verily, we are ruined!",
      "numberInSurah": 66,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5046,
      "text": "Nay, but we have been deprived [of our livelihood]!”",
      "numberInSurah": 67,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5047,
      "text": "Have you ever considered the water which you drink?",
      "numberInSurah": 68,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5048,
      "text": "Is it you who cause it to come down from the clouds - or are We the cause of its coming down?",
      "numberInSurah": 69,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5049,
      "text": "[It comes down sweet - but] were it Our will, We could make it burningly salty and bitter: why, then, do you not give thanks [unto Us]?",
      "numberInSurah": 70,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5050,
      "text": "Have you ever considered the fire which you kindle?",
      "numberInSurah": 71,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5051,
      "text": "Is it you who have brought into being the tree that serves as its fuel - or are We the cause of its coming into being?",
      "numberInSurah": 72,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5052,
      "text": "It is We who have made it a means to remind [you of Us], and a comfort for all who are lost and hungry in the wilderness [of their lives].",
      "numberInSurah": 73,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5053,
      "text": "Extol, then, the limitless glory of thy Sus­tainer’s mighty name!",
      "numberInSurah": 74,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5054,
      "text": "NAY, I call to witness the coming-down in parts [of this Qur’an]",
      "numberInSurah": 75,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5055,
      "text": "and, behold, this is indeed a most solemn affirmation, if you but knew it!",
      "numberInSurah": 76,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5056,
      "text": "Behold, it is a truly noble discourse,",
      "numberInSurah": 77,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5057,
      "text": "[conveyed unto man] in a well-guarded divine writ",
      "numberInSurah": 78,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5058,
      "text": "which none but the pure [of heart] can touch:",
      "numberInSurah": 79,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5059,
      "text": "a revelation from the Sustainer of all the worlds!",
      "numberInSurah": 80,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5060,
      "text": "Would you, now, look down with disdain on a tiding like this,",
      "numberInSurah": 81,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5061,
      "text": "and make it your daily bread [as it were] to call the truth a lie?",
      "numberInSurah": 82,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5062,
      "text": "Why, then, when [the last breath] comes up to the throat [of a dying man],",
      "numberInSurah": 83,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5063,
      "text": "the while you are [helplessly] looking on -",
      "numberInSurah": 84,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5064,
      "text": "and while We are closer to him than you, although you see [Us] not -:",
      "numberInSurah": 85,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5065,
      "text": "why, then, if [you think that] you are not truly dependent [on Us],",
      "numberInSurah": 86,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5066,
      "text": "can you not cause that [ebbing life] to return - if what you claim is true?",
      "numberInSurah": 87,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5067,
      "text": "[ALL OF YOU are destined to die.] Now if one happens to be of those who are drawn close unto God,",
      "numberInSurah": 88,
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
